{"tid":1795703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美眾議員約霍：很好的見到我的朋友邵嵐講述「不要購買中國製造產品」的政策","createTime":"2019-12-24T06:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T06:29:10.000Z","uid":92301,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fdad4dcc91c1fe95d06fa65465bda2d429b4a4d9","tid":1795703,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBY9RrN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBY9RrN.jpg&h=d37a6f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RepTedYoho/status/1209139386211880960?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepTedYoho%2Fstatus%2F1209139386211880960%3Fs%3D19&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpgogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=09592f17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepTedYoho%2Fstatus%2F1209139386211880960%3Fs%3D19&h=677f61fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RepTedYoho/status/1209139386211880960?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"f96677031de86f85459185edd6ea30f94aba3eb7","tid":1795703,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去大半年，大家既生活都過得好壓抑，好似見到有希望但係又唔知前路候點。有人或者係依大半年同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手離婚，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸又或者有家歸不得，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpgogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=3f63be36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0c7791ae2f32742ac02790526625421f4c7144","tid":1795703,"uid":302917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:16:27.000Z","msg":"#AnywhereButChina<br />\n#BoycottMadeInChina<br />\n<br />\n唔單止自己做，仲要推到全球一齊做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2d2186e641e30f55a39e7a72143e36f84bae73","tid":1795703,"uid":32675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:17:03.000Z","msg":"abc<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab18f815225b5fc4b00307860d02534d5a1b8de","tid":1795703,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:21:57.000Z","msg":"推!!!"},{"pid":"25b0d1cee365911fc756f9e67fdaca4712a11a38","tid":1795703,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:25:30.000Z","msg":"Abc 煲大個潮流"},{"pid":"eee98c1a680144803b2f10a9de216ad52beea020","tid":1795703,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:27:11.000Z","msg":"幾好  識到人<br />\n<br />\n為長遠國際戰線 鋪路"},{"pid":"a63abb5a5471b0caaae21e481a66a934ab4f08d7","tid":1795703,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:28:51.000Z","msg":"潮流唔興買支那製產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5d2d8c453d5d2e70a9b9ef8fa646ab99b054ba","tid":1795703,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:29:10.000Z"